Package datalog

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Condition
    This class stores all information on conditions of a datalog rule.
    Fact
    This class stores all information of datalog edb and idb facts - edb facts are values which are stored in the database and known at the beginning - idb facts are derived values from datalog rules.
    MagicCondition
    This class generates magic conditions.
    MigrationExecution
    This is a superclass for TopDownExecution with similar methods for both migration approaches: bottom up (not implemented yet!)
    PairForMagicCondition
    This class stores kind and position values based on Magic Condition.
    Predicate
    This is a class for representing datalog predicates.
    Rule
    This is a class for representing a datalog rule.
    RuleBody
    This class represents the rule body of a datalog rule, a rule body consists of several predicates and their conditions.
